trans-unit.source: Enables iteration over a collection of <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects.

Use the XmlSchemaEnumerator to perform for-each iterations over a collection of <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects contained by an instance of the <xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas> class.
trans-unit.target: 使用 XmlSchemaEnumerator 的<xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>对象包含的<xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas>类</xref:System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas>实例的</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>集合上执行的每个迭代

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemaEnumerator"></xref> class.
The <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemas"></xref> object you want to iterate over.
Gets the current element in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 获取集合中的当前元素。

trans-unit.source: The current <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> object in the collection.
Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.Xml.Serialization.XmlSchemaEnumerator"></xref>.
Advances the enumerator to the next item in the collection.
trans-unit.target: 将枚举数推进到集合中的下一项。

Sets the enumerator to its initial position, which is before the first element in the collection of <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> objects.
